{"tid":1983610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當着防線警自瀆　越南漢獲判罰款了事","createTime":"2020-04-22T03:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T03:29:48.000Z","uid":35562,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f740ea6cc0f790e56e190c0d1d1bfbe61348af3","tid":1983610,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"去年10月31日大批市民聚集旺角街頭，警方於彌敦道設立防線應對，惟一名醉酒越南中年漢竟走到防線前，拉開褲鍊當着警員面前套弄陽具。該越南男子今日（21日）在西九龍法院承認在公眾地方作出猥褻行為罪，求情指因母親離世情緒大受影響，事發前飲了6罐啤酒消愁，受酒精響下才會犯案。裁判官考慮到被告認罪，判處他罰款2000港元。<br />\n50歲越南籍被告趙文俊，持香港身份證，報稱是臨時清潔工。案情指，去年10月31日有人在旺角彌敦道與鴉蘭街交界聚集，至晚上10時許，被告穿過集結人群走到警方防線前約3米位置，並拉下牛仔褲的褲鏈。警員見狀試圖喝止，惟被告充耳不聞，更取出陽具，用右手緊握前後移動7至8下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200421/bkn-20200421151425787-0421_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200421%2Fbkn-20200421151425787-0421_00822_001.html&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8vrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=9b6bd2ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200421/bkn-20200421151425787-0421_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e233295e66938dc6fc008c05545d53ae5f4991a4","tid":1983610,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"行為藝術"},{"pid":"7bb73ec5e03744200293f7fbde40041d1d14cf62","tid":1983610,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"防暴警：比你身份證同電話號碼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b28ff5e0190eecdfc7cc97c2cf71fbf316ba00","tid":1983610,"uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7bb73ec5e03744200293f7fbde40041d1d14cf62","tid":1983610,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"防暴警：比你身份證同電話號碼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"屌, 加左最後個符號&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" 